==English==

===Etymology===
Frequentive of ''[[fond]]''.

===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /ˈfɒndl/
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɒndəl|-ɒndəl]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb|fondles|fondling|fondled|fondled}}
# To touch or [[stroke]] [[lovingly]].
#:''Mothers '''fondle''' their babies.''
# To [[grasp]].
#:''The lovers '''fondled''' each other.''

